Charities exist for a social purpose and to be drives of social change.  The Greater Pittsburgh Nonprofit Partnership exists to improve the viability, impact, and effectiveness of the sector.  We do this through:
- Educating the public about the nonprofit sector and generating support for the sector;
- Acting as an informed, organized voice for the sector;
